    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>
      Heart Rate Tracking Alarm does <strong>not collect, store, or share</strong> any personal data.
    </p>
    <p>
      The app connects to Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) heart rate monitors to read heart rate values in real time.
      All data is processed locally on your device and is never transmitted, stored externally, or shared.
    </p>
    <p>
      The app does not use analytics, tracking, advertising SDKs, or third-party data collection services.
    </p>
    <p>
      Notifications are used solely to alert you when your heart rate exceeds or falls below user-defined thresholds.
    </p>

